quran[339]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,Nyang han tem pateh rumpok ngon Kar Awak nyan meunoe teuma jipeugah Kon malaikat geupeutron keunoe Ubak geutanyoe geuba peurintah Atawa taeu Tuhan geutanyoe Keubit awak nyoe teukabo leupah Jipike keudroe sang jih that raya Jidarohaka lalem sileupah
  25,22,Uroe nyan jieu treuk malaikat i Hana le mangat jeuet jih beulisah Gadoh geumbira ngon keuseunangan Bandum awak nyan nyang peubuet salah Jikheun hai tuboh nyan jrakeuh jinoe
  25,23,Amai jih jinoe Kamoe eu bagah Han le meuguna keu jih amai nyan Bandum di sinan abeh meuruah Ka jeuet keu abee jipo meukeupoi
  25,24,Ureueng nyang beutoi teuma meutuah Asoe churuga bandum ureueng nyan Seunang ngon aman hana ban peugah Teumpat geu-eh-eh watee cot uroe Takalon bagoe leupah that indah
  25,25,Uroe nyan beukah meukuak langet ; Awan jiteubiet bak langet beukah Malaikat dum geuyue tron keunoe
  25,26,Keurajeuen jinoe cit sidroe Allah Keurajeuen nyang hak sit milek Tuhan Kaphe uroe nyan meukarat leupah
  25,27,Teuma si lalem jikap ngon jaroe Jikheun uroe nyoe leupah that sosah Adak meu dilee lon jak ngon Rasul Meuhat leubeh phui hana that payah
  25,28,Keupeue si paleh lon cok keu rakan Ceulaka badan jinoe that sosah
  25,29,"Jipeusisat lon bek ingat Tuhan : Geujok Qur’an jiyue tiek bagah 9 Jipeungeut teupat insan le chetan ‘Oh Iheueh jipadan droe jih jipeuglah"
  25,30,Pakri kaom lon wahe Tuhanku i Rasul meungadu keudeh bak Allah Jikheun Qur’an nyoe hana laku Hana meunapsu jitueng phaedah
  25,31,Meunankeuh musoh bandum Kamoe bri Nyang lawan Nabi sit awak salah Cukop Po gata nyang bri peutunyok Gata pih Neucok Neutulong bagah
  25,32,Jikheun le kaphe pakon han sigo ; Geupeutron laju Qur’an beu bagah Kamoe peukeumat lam ate gata Mangat got meusra bek le meuruah Nyang jeuet keuh meunan Kamoe yue baca Bek sigo teuka gadoh dum bagah
  25,33,Watee na peue-peue jiba bak gata à Meubri keu gata jalan tapeuglah £ Jalan nyang beuna tapeugah bak jih Tapeutrang bak jih nyang got that leupah
  25,34,Teuma awak nyan ‘oh geupeusapat Muka jih meuhat geulungkop bagah Geulungkop laju dalam nuraka Teumpat ceulaka hana ban peugah Keunankeuh jalan nyang leupah sisat
  25,35,Jinoe riwayat Musa meutuah Kamoe bri kitab dilee keu Musa Ngon Harun dua geuba peurintah Aduen geuh Harun keu wazir gopnyan
  25,36,Kamoe kheun yoh nyan jak keudeh bagah Ubak kaom nyan tajak bandua Teuh jih dum nyata raya that salah Jipeugah sulet dum ayat Kamoe Binasa jinoe bandum jih sudah
  25,37,Kaom Noh jikheun sulet dum Rasul é Meugasui-gasui lam laot luah Kamoe peukaram bandum jih sinan Mangat dum insan jitueng phaedah Azeueb peudeh that Kamoe seudia Keu si elanya nyang lalem leupah
  25,38,‘Ad lom ngon Tsamud bandum jih saban Kaom Ras meunan sit hana ubah Meunan pih le lom kurun nyang laen Di antara nyan bandum buet salah
  25,39,Kamoe peugot jih dum keu ibarat Soe nyang tem ingat raya phaedah Kamoe peuanco jih bandum reule Meusapeue tan le ka abeh sudah
  25,40,Ka lagi jijak dalam nanggroe nyan Nyang na disinan euncit ujeuen rhah Kon jieu euncit ujeuen ceulaka Jipeubinasa kaom nyang salah Teutapi dijih han cit jipateh Geubangket dum jih dudoe geubalah
  25,41,‘Oh jieu gata cit ka ji batok Jiulok-ulok jikhem meuhah-hah 2 Nyoe roe ureuengjih keubit keu Rasul Sang leupah that phui meunan jipeugah
  25,42,Rap jipeusisat bandum geutanyoe Tuhan geutanyoe dum jikheun salah Lah pih tasaba taseumah sabe Adak han tan le peue nyang taseumah d Jiteupeue teuma ‘oh jieu azeueb Si nyang bit sisat jalan ka salah
  25,43,Taci peugah soe peutuhan napsu Jipeubuet laju peue napsu peugah Ek tatem gata tapeulahra jih
  25,44,Peue tasangka jih jideungo leupah 7 Peue tasangka jih nyan na meuakai Hana roe sagai akai jih ceudah 7 Jih nyan saban that lagee binatang Leubeh lom jih nyan sisat that leupah
  25,45,Peue hana taeu pakri di Tuhan Neubri bubayangteuh panyang leupah Meunyo Neukheundak ek Neupeuteutap Bubayang meuhat han Neupeuleumah. Dimata uroe nyan jeuet keu dali Bubayang meuri taeu trang leupah
  25,46,Lheueh nyan seuen bacut Kamoe cok bayang Kakeuh bubayang hana le leumah
  25,47,Tuhan nyang peujeuet keu gata malam E Pakaian hitam sang taeu ulah Taeh got teungeut taistirahat ‘Oh uroe meuhat mita nafakah y
  25,48,Neukirem angen haba geumbira Dang-dang troh teuka rahmat bak Allah Kamoe peutren treuk ujeuen di langet Ujeuen nyan rahmat ie gleh sileupah
  25,49,Kamoe peuhudep tanoh nyang mate Hijo dum sare takalon indah Dumna binatang nyang Kamoe peujeuet Meubri ie leugat mangat puleh grah Ke manusia sit le Kamoe bri
  25,50,Kamoe jok bagi jitueng phaedah 3 Teuma nyang le that dum manusia Hana jikira keu rahmat Allah Dijih jikaphe keu rahmat Kamoe
  25,51,Meu na hʻeut Kamoe cit Meujak peugah Meukirem Rasul bak jeuep-jeuep nanggroe Bandum ureueng nyoe jak ba peurintah
  25,52,Teuma bek gata taikot kaphe Tajihad sabe jih nyan tahujjah Ngon dali Qur’an jihad nyang raya
  25,53,Allah Taʻala kuasa leupah ; Dua boh laot Neupeujeuet sapat Saboh tabeue that tajep puleh grah Saboh laot treuk masen ngon phet that Di teungoh meuhat ka Neuboh bataih Bek meujampu ie sinoe ngon sideh Lagee na binteh sang meunan ulah
  25,54,Bak ie jeureuengeh Neupeujeuet insan Jeuet keuturonan jih le that leupah Deungon meukawen jeuet keuturonan Kuasa Tuhan hana ban peugah
  25,55,Teuma jiseumah cit nyang kon Tuhan Nyang keu jih sit tan jibri phaedah Jibri meularat pih han ek keu jih Jiseumah cit jih dikaphe jadah Dikaphe jicok keu ngon jih cheitan Jilawan Tuhan nyang Maha Murah
  25,56,Tauma di-Kamoe Meukirem gata Mangat tajak ba bandum peurintah Haba nyang mangat haba nyang saket
  25,57,Takheun dilon bit kon lon tueng upah t Hana lon lakee upah bak gata Soe nyang tem teuma nyoekeuh lon peugah Soe nyang tem tajak bak jalan Tuhan Nyoekeuh nyang jalan teupat sileupah
  25,58,Tawakkal gata teuma bak Tuhan Hudep beurangjan sidroe-Neuh Allah Nyang han tom mate lom sabe keukai Dari phon awai han tom sudah Takheun Teuseubeh Tuhan tapujoe Neumaklum keudroe soe-soe nyang salah Cukop Neumaklum padum le hamba Nyang peubuet deecha le han ban peugah
  25,59,Tuhan nyang peujeuet langet ngon. bumoe Bandum ngon asoe nam uroe sudah ‘Oh lheueh nam uroe Neupeujeuet abeh Neupiyoh sideh di ateueh ‘arasy Geumaseh that-that Tuhanku sidroe Tatanyong bagoe bak ureueng ceudah Tatanyong bak soe nyang na ileumee Mangat meuteuntee bek jeuet keu salah
  25,60,‘Oh geuyue bak jih sujud keu Tuhan Jikheun toh Tuhan tacuba peugah Peue kamoe sujud bak nyang gata yue Batat jih dum nyoe meutamah-tamah
  25,61,Maha Suci that Tuhan nyang peujeuet Sideh di langet teumpat jisinggah Teumpat jipiyoh dum bintang-bintang Mata uroe trang lom hu sileupah Buleuen meucahya pih trang lam nanggroe
  25,62,Malam ngon uroe Neupisah-pisah Soe nyang tem ingat bandum atra nyan f Chukor le yoh nyan keudeh bak Allah
  25,63,Na hamba Tuhan nyang jak lam bumoe Dum meu glah keudroe han bagah-bagah Geujak ban teupat ban legee seunang Meu na soe tanyong geuseuot bagah Meu narit jahe bak ureueng tanyong Jaweueb digopnyan narit jroh leupah
  25,64,‘Oh watee malam teuma ureueng nyan Sujud bak Tuhan nyang Maha Murah Geudong seumbahyang ingat Po gopnyan
  25,65,Geukheun ya Tuhan kamoe Neupeuglah i Azeueb nuraka bek roh keu kamoe Ya Tuhan kamoe Neubri meusiblah Azeueb nuraka saket meukeumat
  25,66,Sijeuheut teumpat tapiyoh payah Ceulaka teumpat teutap di sinan
  25,67,Teuma ureueng nyan geubri napakah Hana leupah that hana hemat that Di teungoh meuhat sabe geulangkah
  25,68,Hana geupuja tuhan nyang laen Nyawong gop hareuem pih geupeusiblah Hana geupoh gop Tuhan peuhareuem Meulengkan nyang nyan ka hak bak Allah Geupubuet zina hana digopnyan Ureueng peubuet nyan raya that salah Nyang peubuet nyan dum raya that dacha
  25,69,Azeueb Neuganda teuma le Allah Uroe kiamat keukai lam azeueb Sinan hina that hana ban peugah
  25,70,Meulengkan ureueng nyang ka jitoubat Jiiman meuhat pih hana ubah Amai nyang got that jipeubuet sabe £ Ureueng nyan han le lam kawan salah Tuhan Neugantoe amai nyang jeuheut Neupeujeuet keu got bandum le Allah Keubit cit Tuhan Maha Peungampon Lagi pih Tuhan Maha Peumurah
  25,71,Beurangsoe toubat peubuet amai got Nyankeuh nyang toubat keubit bak Allah
  25,72,Han geu-ek saksi meunyo nyang sulet Hana meu siblet pih geutem peugah Watee geukalon buet sia-sia Sagai han teuka keunan geulangkah Geujaga that droe ureueng mulia Buet sia-sia hana phaedah
  25,73,Soe nyang peuingat teuma ureueng nyan Ngon ayat Tuhan nyang Maha Murah Geudeungo got that kon buta tuloe
  25,74,Geukheun lom meunoe wahe ya Allah Hai Tuhan kamoe Neubri keu kamoe Dum judo kamoe ureueng meutuah d Meunan pih aneuk ngon cuco kamoe Bak mata kamoe beu sijuek leupah í Teutap ngon mata sijuek ngon ate Sabab boh ate ureueng nyang ceudah Neupeujeuet kamoe jeuet keu peumuka Keu ureueng takwa keupada Allah
  25,75,Ureueng nyan bandum Neubri balasan Teuma le Tuhan churuga indah y Sabab ureueng nyan ek that geusaba Neupeumulia teuma le Allah Geusambot gopnyan dum ngon hormat Saleuem seulamat jak tamong bagah
  25,76,Keukai di sinan teumpat indah that Neubri ngon pangkat manyang that leupah y
  25,77,Takheun Tuhan lon han Neungieng gata Sabab kon gata ureueng meutuah Meunyo han tatem pubuet ibadat Sulet ngon jeungkat nyang na di babah Sabab nyan gata teuntee geuazeueb d Ban lagee nyang buet masa nyang sudah y 7 ASY-SYUʻARA‘ (UREUENG-UREUENG ME Ngon nama Allah lon peuphon surat Tuhan Hadharat nyang Maha Murah Tuhanku Sidroe geumaseh that-that Donya akhirat rahmat Neulimpah)
  26,1,Tha Sin Mim Tuhan nyang teupeue meukeusud ayat Sabab Hadharat hana Neupeugah
  26,2,Nyoekeuh dum ayat di dalam kitab Qur’an nyoe meuhat cit trang sileupah
  26,3,Sang-sang digata gadoh seumangat Watee taingat jipeubuet salah Pakon jih batat han jimeuiman
  26,4,Sabe sit meunan dum kaphe jadah Meu Kamoe kheundak Meupeutron ayat Saboh muʻjizat nyang hebat leupah Sideh di langet Meupeutron ayat Mangat jih teupat jiteukui bagah
  26,5,Beurangpeue ayat teuka lom bak jih Teutap sit dijih hana jipapah Ayat nyang baro teuka bak Tuhan Han jipeureumeun jipaleng bagah
  26,6,Ka jikheun sulet han jitem pateh Dudoe bak droejih teuma geupeugah Bandum geubalah teuma nyan dijih Nyang jipeu-eleh jikheun beurakah
  26,7,Peue hana jieu di dalam bumoe Bak kayee sinoe hijo dum indah Kamoe peuudep dumna tanaman Meupasang-pasang galakteuh leupah
  26,8,Bandum atra nyan sit jeuet keu tanda Allah Taʻala Maha Peumurah Teuma le that jih han jimeuiman Dijih bandum nyan hana phaedah
  26,9,Keubit Po gata Maha Peurkasa Lom pih Po gata Maha Peumurah
  26,10,Watee Neumeuhei uleh Po gata b4 Tajak hai Musa keudeh talangkah 4 Kaom nyang lalem kaphe keu Tuhan
  26,11,Kaom Peuraʻeun nyang that seurakah Pakon bandum jih han jitakwa
  26,12,Geukheun le Musa wahe ya Allah Lon takot sulet jipeugah keu lon Han jipateh lon jikheun beurakah
  26,13,Seumpet dada lon han glah lidah lon Neukirem Harun lom Neuyue peugah
  26,14,Dilon na salah pih bak awak nyan Takot jipoh lon jimeung tueng balah
  26,15,Neukheun hana peue tajak bandua Ò Kamoe bri tanda nyang raya tuah Kamoe Meudeungo peue-peue nyang jikheun
  26,16,Ubak Peuraʻeun keudeh tapeugah Kamoe nyoe Rasul Tuhan Po alam
  26,17,Awak kamoe nyan Neuyue peuleupah Bani Israil tajok keu kamoe
  26,18,Jiseuot meunoe laju jipeugah Kon gata dilee kamoe peulahra Yoh mantong gata si manyak mirah Padum thon sabe taduek ngon kamoe
  26,19,Tapeubuet dudoe buet nyang that salah oi Dum guna kamoe hana tapike Tatem jak kaphe hana tapeugah
  26,20,Geukheun buet lon nyan sabab meularat Watee nyan sisat lon ka roh salah
  26,21,Nyankeuh jeuet lon plueng keudeh u lua Takot keu gata tameung tueng balah Teuma di sideh Tuhan bri keu lon Hikmah keu lon Neubri got leupah Neupeujeuet treuk lon keu Rasul Tuhan
  26,22,Teuma nikmat nyan nyang gata peugah Tapeulahra lon yoh mantong ubit Ka tapeunamiet dum hamba Allah Bani Israil dum tapeunamiet Lalem that keubit elanya leupah
  26,23,Peuraʻeun tanyong boh nyang toh Tuhan Nyang Po dum alam bunoe tapeugah
  26,24,Geukheun Tuhan Po langet ngon bumoe Ngon bandum asoe bandum blah bicah Meu tatem pateh nyankeuh nyang Tuhan
  26,25,Peuraʻeun jikheun bak ngon jih bagah Nyan na tadeungo roe gata bandum
  26,26,Musa kheun Tuhan kuasa leupah Tuhan gata dum ngon yah-yah gata Nyang dilee masa dum ka beh leupah
  26,27,Jikheun Rasul nyan nyang jak bak gata Jih nyan ka gila akai ka ubah
  26,28,Geukheun Tuhan Po timu ngon barat Bandum lat batat peuneujeuet Allah Meunyo tapike ngon akai nyang got
  26,29,Jikheun bek le that haba tapeugah Meu takheun tuhan laen nibak lon Gata lam palong keudeh kukeubah Dalam glap seupot kupasoe gata
  26,30,Teuma kheun Musa deungo lon peugah Meunyo ek lon bri dali nyang nyata Teuma peue gata tatem meunyeurah
  26,31,Jikheun jok keunoe dali bak gata Meunyo bit beuna lagee tapeugah
  26,32,Geutiek treuk tungkat ka jeuet keu naga Uleue be raya nyata that leupah
  26,33,Geusuet ngon jaroe puteh meukeuprak Soe nyang ngieng rusak mata jih mirah
  26,34,Jikheun treuk laju bak rakan lingka Nyoe sihe raya carong jih leupah
  26,35,Jimeung peuteubiet gata lam nanggroe Teuh ngon sihe nyoe gata jirajah Boh peue tapeugot teuma keu jih nyoe
  26,36,Tayue preh jih nyoe teuma jipeugah Í Ngon aduen jih nyan tayue preh siat Ditanyoe rakyat jinoe dum takrah Ban saboh nanggroe meusapat keunoe
  26,37,Sihe geutanyoe pih carong leupah d Sihe nyang utoh bandum tayue jak
  26,38,Bandum treuk jijak keunan dum bagah Bak watee uroe nyang ka jimaklum
  26,39,Jitanyong bandum ka troh talangkah
  26,40,Mangat taikot bandum sihe nyan Meunyo ek meunang lagee jipeugah
  26,41,‘Ohban troh keunan dum tukang sihe Ka jitanyong le jilakee upah Jilakee upah ubak Peuraʻeun Meu kamoe meunang peue na hadiah
  26,42,Jikheun hadiah cit na keu gata Gata ngon raja lom toe that leupah
  26,43,Geukheun le Musa boh tiek peue nyang na Nyang keunoe taba ‘oh Iheueh tarajah
  26,44,Jitiek treuk taloe ngon tungkat jih dum Deumi Peuraʻeun raja nyang meugah Geutanyoe meunang meunan dum jikheun
  26,45,Geutiek treuk keunan tungkat meutuah ‘Ohban ka geutiek tungkat le Musa Jiʻuet treuk sigra peue nyang meurimbah Abeh dum jiʻuet sihe awak nyan
  26,46,Teukeujet yoh nyan tukang meurajah Si tukang sihe bandum jisujud Í Sabab teukeujet jikalon ulah
  26,47,Jikheun treuk bandum kamoe meuiman Tuhan Po alam kuasa leupah
  26,48,Tuhan Po Musa ngon Tuhan Harun
  26,49,Beungeh Peuraʻeun jikheun treuk bagah Peue kameuiman laju keu jih nyan Gohlom kuizin le lon dum keu kah i Keubit gureekah jih nyang raya that Sihe dum meuhat jipeurunoe kah Nyoe beu kateupeue hukoman kubri Jaroe ngon gaki kukoh kutarah Jaroe ngon gaki kusurang sareng Lheueh nyan kupateng beu manyang leupah Bandum kuteupang u ateuh sula Nak bek biasa lawan peurintah
  26,50,Seuot awak nyan hana meularat Kamoe dum meuhat meuwoe bak Allah Ubak Po kamoe keudeh dum muewoe
  26,51,Neuampon kamoe meulakee bagah Raya that deecha kamoe baroekon Kamoe meuiman jinoe ya Allah Nyoekeuh dum kamoe nyang phon meuiman
  26,52,Bak Musa yoh nyan Kamoe kheun bagah Bak watee malam tateubiet sigra Bandum ngon hamba Lon nyang meutuah Gata nyoe bandum jilet di likot
  26,53,Keubit jiseutot Peuraʻeun jadah Bansaboh nanggroe jikrah dum rakyat
  26,54,Awak nyan meuhat sit nit sileupah
  26,55,Jimeung peubeungeh bandum geutanyoe
  26,56,Tajaga jih nyoe beu got that leupah
  26,57,Kamoe peuteubiet treuk bandum jih nyan Tinggai treuk taman jih dum nyang luah Tinggai mata ie teumpat jimanoe
  26,58,Geudong meuasoe bandum jikeubah Tinggai dum pangkat jih nyang mulia
  26,59,Bandum pusaka tinggai le leupah Kamoe bri bandum keu cot Israil
  26,60,Dijih peureugi jiseutot bagah Ka teubiet uroe keudeh jiseutot
  26,61,‘Oh ban meusapat jieu ka leumah Geukheun dum yoh nyan le rakan Musa Musoh ka teuka jehpat le leupah Tanyoe jiteumee han jipeulheueh le
  26,62,Musa geukheun le bek sosah-sosah Tuhan lon sajan Neutunyok keu lon À Sit Neubri jalan tanyoe Neupeuglah
  26,63,Kamoe bri wahyu teuma bak Musa Nyan tungkat gata tapoh ie bagah Tapoh ie laot ngon tungkat gata Teuhah le sigra jalan dum luah Sang gunong raya dum dalam laot Meuikot-ikot gata meung bagah
  26,64,Awak nyang seutot teuma di likot Kamoe peuikot ka toe that leupah
  26,65,Kamoe peuleupah Musa ngon rakan
  26,66,Laen dum karam lam laot luah
  26,67,Bandum atra nyan sit jeuet keu tanda Allah Taʻala kuasa leupah < Teuma le that jih han jimeuiman Dijih bandum nyan hana phaedah>
  26,68,Keubit Po gata Maha Peurkasa Lom pih Po gata Maha Peumurah
  26,69,Teuma tapeugah lom bak awak nyan Haba Ibrahim ureueng meutuah
  26,70,Geukheun bak ayahgeuh ngon bak kaom d Geuh gata bandum peue nyan taseumah
  26,71,Jikheun dum kamoe meuseumah patong Beurhala bandum han kamoe keubah
  26,72,Geukheun boh na deuh jideungo gata Watee tabaca peue tameung peugah
  26,73,Ek jibri le jih peue nyang munapheu“ʻat í Got pih meularat teuh ek jipeuglah
  26,74,Jikheun dum kamoe meu-eu yah kamoe Bandum atra nyoe dilee geuseumah A
  26,75,Geukheun taeukeuh nyang taseumah nyan
  26,76,Le gata dum nyan ngon ayah-ayah Ngon yah-yah gata dum nyang ka dilee
  26,77,Bandum nyan sitree lon musoh leupah 1 Meulengkan Tuhan nyang Po alam nyoe
  26,78,Nyang peujeuet lon nyoe phon manyak leupah Neubri peutunyok keu lon ‘oh lheueh nyan
  26,79,Neubri makanan ngon ie puleh grah
  26,80,Watee saket lon Neupeupuleh le
  26,81,Lon Neupeumate pih han soe teugah Neupeuudep lon lom ‘oh Iheueh mate
  26,82,Neuampon sabe watee lon salah Meunapsu lon that Neuampon dacha Jan haro hara watee Neubalah Uroe kiamat haro hara that
  26,83,Neubri hikmat keu lon ya Allah € Neupeusapat lon ngon ureueng shaleh
  26,84,Neupeujroh leubeh nan lon gop peugah Bak ureueng dudoe nan lon beu beuna
  26,85,Neubri pusaka churuga indah Churuga nikmat lon tueng pusaka Neubri keu hamba wahe ya Allah
  26,86,Lom Neupeuampon dacha ayah lon Sabab ayah lon sisat ka salah
  26,87,Lom pih ulon nyoe bek Neubri ‘ayeb Uroe geubangket malee lon leupah
  26,88,Atra ngon aneuk hana guna le ‘Oh uroe page ka teuka sudah
  26,89,Meulengkan soe-soe nyang jak bak Tuhan Ate jih iman nyang gleh sileupah
  26,90,Teuma geupeutoe keunan churuga Bak ureueng takwa iman keu Allah
  26,91,Diureueng sisat leumah nuraka
  26,92,Geutanyong sigra ho ka tuhankah Peue nyang ka seumah nyang bukan Tuhan
  26,93,Ho ka dum jih nyan kacuba peugah ž Na jitulong kah atawa droejih
  26,94,Geulungkop dum jih lam apui mirah Awak nyang sisat meusapat ngon jih
  26,95,Lom tentra Iblih sinan geukeubah Sipai Iblih bandum di sinan
  26,96,Meudawa yoh nyan meuplah-plah babah
  26,97,Deumi nyo Tuhan kamoe nyoe sisat
  26,98,Gata dum meuhat kamoe jak seumah Sabab meupeusa gata ngon Tuhan Nyang Po dum alam nyang Maha Murah
  26,99,Kon ureueng laen peusisat kamoe Nyoekeuh awak nyoe nyang peubuet salah
  26,100,Hana chupeuʻat le soe keu kamoe
  26,101,Rakan dum nyang toe pih tan le leumah
  26,102,Adak meu geutem geupeuwoe kamoe Meuiman kamoe jinoe le bagah
  26,103,Bandum atra nyan cit jeuet keu tanda Allah Taʻala Kuasa leupah Teuma le that jih han jimeuiman Keu jih bandum nyan hana phaedah
  26,104,Keubit Po gata Maha Peurkasa Lom pih Po gata Maha Peumurah
  26,105,Kaom Noh jikheun sulet dum Rasul Han jitem kaboe watee Noh peugah
  26,106,Chedara jih Noh geukheun bak jih nyan Pakon gata han takwa keu Allah
  26,107,Lon nyoe bit Rasul jeuet tapeucaya
  26,108,Teuma takwa gata keu Allah Tataʻat keu lon nyang Rasul gata
  26,109,Hana bak gata lon lakee upah Bak Po dum alam upah lon ka na
  26,110,Teuma takwa gata keu Allah Tataʻat keu lon nyang Rasul gata
